{"tid":1857941,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"黃任匡：講到逃兵，除左 721 兩名黑警，其實仲有急症室嘅警崗","createTime":"2020-02-02T11:59:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T12:59:04.000Z","uid":104138,"like":38,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"40d193e51db06650551e41df8b4a74ce0ba89a3e","tid":1857941,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T11:59:37.000Z","msg":"黃任匡Facebook<br />\n<br />\n回帶介紹番：講到逃兵，除左 721 兩名黑警，其實仲有急症室嘅警崗。<br />\n<br />\n呢班逃兵，舊年六月俾人鬧完「涉嫌於醫院非法搜證侵害病人私隱」之後嬲嬲豬，決定罷工，唔覺唔覺已經罷左大半年。直到今日，QE個警崗仲係空空如也。屈小姐諗住幾時將佢地處決？<br />\n<br />\n#忠誠勇毅<br />\n#罷工半年<br />\n#真逃兵<br />\n<br />\n經濟日報【反送中】警方反擊？伊院急症室警崗突關門 告示指有事請打999：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2ROUAtJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ROUAtJ&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9OaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=793ed9ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2ROUAtJ</a><br />\n<br />\n蘋果日報【引渡惡法】警協不滿醫護指警員阻工作「要脅」撤醫院警崗 黃任匡：小學雞：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Ome2Mx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Ome2Mx&d=m5PK5j%2F1EvBSK5XTwnZL9OaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=66cf04ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Ome2Mx</a>"},{"pid":"7c030e42980f2c6db7141bb15386fc8149307b22","tid":1857941,"uid":263905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:05:23.000Z","msg":"緊急召集因航MarcoPolo member！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1857781\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1857781</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c55eaec438cbc70ff78ab5ce9c52e88814729b82","tid":1857941,"uid":252609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:29:28.000Z","msg":"藍色雙重標準<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaa64c3852bf4e194e8ca4e9b015f8848e3cb5f5","tid":1857941,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T12:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"